{"tid":733270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州懸紅「通緝」吸血木蝨王 傳染病症可致心衰竭猝死","createTime":"2018-07-07T15:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:34:24.000Z","uid":13468,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"8785f55b257d4d87a0392dc4175be5bc49a0779f","tid":733270,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"傳染病症可致心衰竭猝死　無疫苗無特效藥　廣州懸紅「通緝」吸血木蝨王 (22:52)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180707/s00004/1530974372606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180707%2Fs00004%2F1530974372606&d=YvTVJCTfRYCzpUORTKdE0wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=847d7678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180707%2Fs00004%2F1530974372606&h=8e6d1ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180707/s00004/1530974372606</a><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，廣州市疾控中心近日懸紅，「通緝」一種會吸食人血的昆蟲「錐蝽」，指其會傳播美洲錐蟲病。該病潛伏期長達數十年，嚴重可致心衰竭甚至猝死，且無預防疫苗，亦無特效藥，故有學者將之稱為「新型愛滋病」。疾控中心呼籲民眾協助捉蟲，捕獲每隻錐蝽可獲8元（人民幣，下同）獎勵金及健康諮詢服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錐蝽在廣州俗稱「木蝨王」，因頭部狹長似錐而得名，成蟲體長約2.5厘米，呈黑或暗褐色，橢圓形，尾部尖或平，腹部側緣有紅或黃斑。由於其幼蟲及成蟲均吸食人血，故又被稱為「接吻蟲」。牠們會叮咬人體，特別喜歡面部皮膚較薄的區域，例如嘴唇、眼瞼等。<br />\n<br />\n廣州市疾控中心表示，錐蝽會傳播美洲錐蟲病。人類感染該病後不易發現，潛伏期長達20至30年，患者於發病急性期會發燒、臉部水腫、淋巴結發炎、貧血；慢性期則常出現心肌炎、心力衰竭、巨食管炎、巨結腸、肺或腦栓塞，甚至猝死。病症確診率低，無預防疫苗，晚期時沒有特效藥可治，故有學者將該病稱為「新型愛滋病」。根據疾控中心資料，該病在南美地區發病情況最嚴重，但鄰近中國的日本亦已有病例。<br />\n<br />\n疾控中心表示，錐蝽多藏身於牆壁或木質物件縫隙等地方，夜間會外出活動。中心指錐蟲病傳染源一旦輸入，極有可能造成本地傳播，故呼籲民眾協助捕捉，捕獲並交出每隻錐蝽，可獲8元獎勵金，疾控中心並會提供健康諮詢服務。<br />\n<br />\n（羊城晚報）"},{"pid":"c20289e5d299d1f024a30f735fd45089e03d8220","tid":733270,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82ad7f682218d6a7a2ce8c42c443cb346bbb53e","tid":733270,"uid":24730,"like":198,"dislike":1,"score":197,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"仆街了，唔好跳嚟香港"},{"pid":"0f49863be4aa381049006ab8ee592466fed90fc8","tid":733270,"uid":164966,"like":218,"dislike":3,"score":215,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"捉蟲有錢收,係中國絕種都似"},{"pid":"cf5f046ae0d9418b27fac406e38de9a2cdd555b3","tid":733270,"uid":8410,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"中國又有大禮送過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5719c8127efc2087e04d5be7d77ae2de9cd2d18","tid":733270,"uid":511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"又準備送禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9523213901b93caddf666236c45efb8e18d7f32","tid":733270,"uid":17606,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"8蚊一隻 上數真係不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c6b54dab668a007f3aa310c14a943ac9cabf0d","tid":733270,"uid":176929,"like":316,"dislike":0,"score":316,"quote":{"pid":"0f49863be4aa381049006ab8ee592466fed90fc8","tid":733270,"uid":164966,"like":218,"dislike":3,"score":215,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"捉蟲有錢收,係中國絕種都似"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"傻啦，係都捉黎繁殖去換錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e577f04db7dd2ea5b97b74e1db0182c925a05c","tid":733270,"uid":89514,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c372c37644e71905caad295a6d6d1618f976fac6","tid":733270,"uid":11097,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"香港差不多7成傢私舖都搵大陸做<br />\n咁咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\